ws/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">来庆祝 Oasis 开创性的《Definitely Maybe》30 周年</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> JORJA SMITH……前往 2024 年雷丁和利兹参加英国独家音乐节<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f525.png" alt="🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>周五雷丁/周六利兹</p><p>明天早上 8.30 发售<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/RandL24?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#RandL24</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/JorjaSmith?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@JorjaSmith</a> <a href="https://t.co/5QuCQ6ZyM4">pic.twitter.com/5QuCQ6ZyM4</a></p><p> - 雷丁和利兹节 (@OfficialRandL) <a href="https://twitter.com/OfficialRandL/status/1729929162016645252?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 29 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">英国首个 21 Savage 音乐节公告<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/203c.png" alt="‼" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>添加到周日阅读/周五利兹。门票明天上午 8.30 发售。 <a href="https://twitter.com/21savage?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@21savage</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/RandL24?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#RandL24</a> <a href="https://t.co/0nQdNqIUf5">pic.twitter.com/0nQdNqIUf5</a></p><p> - 雷丁和利兹节 (@OfficialRandL) <a href="https://twitter.com/OfficialRandL/status/1729928285264425005?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 29 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">添加到周五阅读/周六利兹： <a href="https://twitter.com/the_prodigy?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@THE_PRODIGY</a> <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f41c.png" alt="🐜" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;"